## The Non-Negotiable Core Loop

```
Recall ‚Üí Focus ‚Üí Go-To Swap ‚Üí Track Usage ‚Üí Win
```

Every feature must support this cycle. Do not suggest changes that break it.

## Key Constraints

1. **ONE Weekly Focus at a Time** - Never suggest multi-select or parallel focuses
2. **No Dead-Ends** - Every screen must lead somewhere actionable
3. **The Trade Model** - Always frame swaps as trading bad food FOR good combo (not restriction)
4. **Paywall Placement** - Tab 3 (Swaps) is paywalled. Tab 1 & 2 are free
5. **Persistence** - Weekly Focus stays visible and active all week

## Tab Structure (3 Tabs)

- **Tab 1: Recall** - Food logging (Always Free)
- **Tab 2: Insights** - Weekly Focus selection + opportunities (Free with upsell potential)
- **Tab 3: Swaps** - Blue Jay Combos (PAYWALLED - this is the value)

